source.name: RSS Feed for Graphical Tropical Weather Outlooks
source.description: The National Weather Service (NWS) National Hurricane Center uses regularly updated RSS feeds to disseminate tropical weather outlooks for the North Atlantic , Caribbean Sea, Gulf of Mexico, and Eastern Pacific Oceans.
